    "Over time, binding rules with oversight 2 The popularity of ChatGPT represents a prime case revealing policy gaps regarding influential AI systems [158,159,166].",
    "Harm considerations include exposure of personal information through conversations; reinforcement of biases from web-scraped training data; overstated confidence in responses leading to public disinformation; potential to automate phishing, spam, misinformation campaigns; exacerbating cheating in academia and assessments; facilitating creation of malware/ransomware; legal risks regarding IP, defamation and more [78,95,133,142,156,165,179,186].",
